# ============================================
# Monorepo - Bases Meteorologicas La Pampa
# ============================================

# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*

# --- Build outputs ---
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/

# --- Env / secrets ---
# NUNCA subir archivos .env con credenciales reales
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.local.example
# Supabase migrations env files
supabase/.env.dev
supabase/.env.prod

# --- Backups (se generan localmente, no subir al repo) ---
supabase/backups/

# --- Vercel ---
**/.vercel

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Editor / IDE ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Arduino ---
arduino/**/build/
arduino/**/*.bin
arduino/**/*.hex
arduino/.DS_Store

# --- TypeScript ---
*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# --- Misc ---
*.pem
coverage/

# --- Docker runtime data (volumes persistidos) ---
# Los volumenes estan en /var/lib/docker, no en el repo, pero por si acaso:
docker-data/
